<p style="color:#ccffcc";><strong><ins>FEATURED TRACK:</ins></strong> <a href="http://www.torntracks.com/stop_maps" target="_blank">Torn Tracks #14 - Ålesund (3-7 Oct 2018)</a><br></p>

<p>For <a href="https://www.facebook.com/vestlandsutstillingen/" target="_blank">Vestlandsutstillingen 2019</a>, Huizing is developing 6 site specific sound pieces for exhibitions in
  Ålesund, Haugesund, Øystese, Stavanger, Førde and Bergen.</p>
<p>Between 3-7 October 2018, she went on a site visit to Ålesund to explore and record material for this
  new sound piece, the first one of the six. <em>Torn Tracks #14 - Ålesund (3-7 Oct 2018)</em> premiered on
  the opening of the exhibition at KUBE, on the 8th of February and was also performed live there.</p>

<p style="color:#ccffcc";><strong><ins>NEW:</ins></strong> <a href="http://www.torntracks.com/stop_maps" target="_blank">Sketch Maps</a><br></p>
<p>In addition to the 6 new sound pieces, Huizing is developing the website as well. <em>Sketch maps</em> is a new
  way of searching the collection, where one track can have several side tracks or stops.
  More info on this view can be found on its own page.</p>

